</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">(1) 指定一个误差范围，两个浮点数的差值在此范围之内，则认为是相等的。
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"> float a = 1.0f - 0.9f;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"> float b = 0.9f - 0.8f;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"> float diff = 1e-6f;
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl"> if (Math.abs(a - b) &lt; diff) {
</span></span><span class="line"><span class="cl">     System.out.println(&#34;true&#34;);
